Dear Customer,
Thank you for contacting the City of Philadelphia's 311 Contact Center about obtaining a marriage license. A marriage license can be obtained at City Hall, room 413 on Monday, Tuesday, Thursday and Friday from 8:00am to 4:30pm and Friday from 8:00am to 4:00pm. For more information related to marriage licenses visit our website at http://www.phila.gov/311/findananswer/Pages/default.aspx 24 hours a day, where you can find answers to many questions related to City government services in the "Find an Answer" section. Please let us know if we can be of further assistance.
Regards, Philly311 Customer Support
